    "content": "By many this home field has been shamefully neglected, and it is time that divine resources and remedies were presented, that this state of evil may be corrected.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"6T 429.1\" data-link=\"118.2364\">Testimonies for the Church 6:429, 430</span>.</span></a></sup>",
