    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Children to Extend Knowledge of Bible Principles</strong>&mdash;Children who have been properly educated, who love to be useful, to help father and mother, will extend a knowledge of correct ideas and Bible principles to all with whom they associate.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Lt 28, 1890\" data-link=\"14056.6843001\">Letter 28, 1890</span>.</span></a></sup>",
