    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Parents, upon you rests the responsibility of being light-bearers and light-givers. Shine as lights in the home, brightening the path that your children must travel. As you do this, your light will shine to those without.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 1-29-1901\" data-link=\"821.19996\">The Review and Herald, January 29, 1901</span>.</span></a></sup>",
