    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Good Men Needed More Than Great Minds</strong>&mdash;The happiness of families and churches depends upon home <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"38\"></span> influences. Eternal interests depend upon the proper discharge of the duties of this life. The world is not so much in need of great minds as of good men who will be a blessing in their homes.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">14<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"4T 522.1\" data-link=\"114.2572\">Testimonies for the Church 4:522</span>.</span></a></sup>",
