    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "A lack of courtesy, a moment of petulance, a single rough, thoughtless word, will mar your reputation, and may close the door to hearts so that you can never reach them.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">16<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 335.1\" data-link=\"113.1691\">Testimonies for the Church 5:335</span>.</span></a></sup>",
